import { Navbar, Container, Nav, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";

export const TopNav = () => {
    return(
        <Navbar>
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">André Miranda</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav" >
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link">Link</Nav.Link>
                        <NavDropdown title="Social Networks" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Facebook</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Instagram</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Linkedin</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">GitHub</NavDropdown.Item>
                        </NavDropdown>
                    </Nav>

                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    )
}
